』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：今日咁嘅天氣著褸嘅人應該退出連登"},{"pid":"5fc1236d4b7eefe61e2e151b82363a2c4547b9bd","tid":1682353,"uid":158145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"樓主身上咁多毛都覺得凍？"},{"pid":"a7a9502c13d09e7c050cfa8012db1f45a0ca0dfe","tid":1682353,"uid":246329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n睇天文台今日25-27度 你同我講凍?<br />\n30度涼35度暖40先叫熱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁岩今日有風叫做涼D咋<br />\n夜晚開窗都有蚊入尼啦 <br />\n咩時候冇蚊就真係叫凍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226e939235d54ccc90353bc12c7a798124594bb6","tid":1682353,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7a9502c13d09e7c050cfa8012db1f45a0ca0dfe","tid":1682353,"uid":246329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n睇天文台今日25-27度 你同我講凍?<br />\n30度涼35度暖40先叫熱?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁岩今日有風叫做涼D咋<br />\n夜晚開窗都有蚊入尼啦 <br />\n咩時候冇蚊就真係叫凍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"咪扮晒嘢啦 明明凍到仆街"},{"pid":"3c23c6c2d069b76e8cc53115016bebdf1f5ef202","tid":1682353,"uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"人哋著咩衫關你撚事？"},{"pid":"520ff7b1f9838479af8b035258b13b81d9e04c88","tid":1682353,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"樓主好on9"},{"pid":"3c682246230b4d6511867ca539c04d74fdda55df","tid":1682353,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520ff7b1f9838479af8b035258b13b81d9e04c88","tid":1682353,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"樓主好on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"牠自認狗"},{"pid":"4735c315bbf8f0c95f3d392